The paper deals with large-scale recommender systems, which are typically studied in the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The focus on efficiency and speed suggests that the paper could also be relevant to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Data Structures (cs.DS) sub-categories. Finally, the use of binary representations and the evaluation of accuracy suggest that the paper could also be relevant to the Database (cs.DB) sub-category.
